									<h2>privacy policy</h2>
								</div>
								<p>This Privacy Policy explains how Discovered, and its affiliates collect, use, and share information from or about you when you use our websites, interactive TV, desktop, mobile applications, and voice-activated assistants, and other services that link to this policy, as well as connected devices (“Discovered, Services”).</p>
								
								<p>As one of the leading media and entertainment companies, we offer Discovered, Services through a wide range of businesses and under many different brands. You can find out more information about Discovered, including a list of our affiliates (“Discovered, Affiliates”), at <a href="https://discovered.tv" class="policies_link" target="_blank">www.Discovered.TV.</a></p>
								
								<p>When you use the Discovered, Services, you agree to the collection, use, and sharing of your information as described in this Privacy Policy.</p>
								
