								<p>For any questions or complaints about this Privacy Policy or our privacy practices, please contact us at <a href="mailto:Contact@Discovered.tv" class="policies_link" target="_blank">Contact@Discovered.tv</a> or Chief Privacy Officer, Discovered, Legal Department, <a href="mailto:Ricky@AttorneyRickyAnderson.com" class="policies_link">Ricky@AttorneyRickyAnderson.com</a>.</p>
